# Analyze Position
# POST /analyze-position
# Analyze a single board position using Katahex raw neural network.
# Accepts arbitrary positions (unequal stone counts allowed).

### Analyze custom position (black to play)
POST {{HEX_AI_DISTRIBUTED_API}}/analyze-position
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "color": "black",
    "size": 14,
    "white": "a1 d4 f5 f7 g9 g11 g14",
    "black": "d5 k2"
}


### Analyze empty board (black to play)
POST {{HEX_AI_DISTRIBUTED_API}}/analyze-position
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "color": "black",
    "size": 11,
    "white": "",
    "black": ""
}
